2d486a48bff0e9e69c653ec289c0a8d4d0180cbfefbdc945308e09de23dc4785163dd39c2b0f6dc58b54b3ab2b993bd96e906c37e28ce4bdff43093fc8008fde  kicad-i18n-5.1.8.tar.gz"
